  "text": "Recently, there have been attempts to combine approaches. [CITATION_1] use an approach based on semantics to perform syntactic simplification, and PBMT for lexical simplifications. We have also created a hybrid system, but one using linguistically sound hand written rules for syntactic simplification and automatically acquired rules for lexicalised constructs . In this paper we combine this work (summarised in §3) with a new method for sentence compression (described in §4).",
